Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 01:59:16 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 06/18] Add TermSurf viewport resize

A headless view learned to resize,
With pixels both humble and wise.
No grand frame parade,
Just a viewport remade,
For Girlbat to stretch toward the skies.
---
 .../LibTermSurfLadybird/TermSurfLadybird.cpp  | 22 ++++++++++++++++++-
 1 file changed, 21 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/Libraries/LibTermSurfLadybird/TermSurfLadybird.cpp b/Libraries/LibTermSurfLadybird/TermSurfLadybird.cpp
index d2df084ec4..5dcd07b557 100644
--- a/Libraries/LibTermSurfLadybird/TermSurfLadybird.cpp
+++ b/Libraries/LibTermSurfLadybird/TermSurfLadybird.cpp
@@ -138,6 +138,11 @@ public:
         ++m_render_surface_generation;
     }
 
+    void resize(Web::DevicePixelSize viewport_size)
+    {
+        reset_viewport_size(viewport_size);
+    }
+
 private:
     TermSurfWebView(Core::AnonymousBuffer theme, Web::DevicePixelSize viewport_size)
         : HeadlessWebView(move(theme), viewport_size)
@@ -186,6 +191,7 @@ extern "C" char const* ts_ladybird_runtime_last_error(TsLadybirdRuntime const*);
